# LaTeX build artifacts under any papers/ dir — regenerable by rebuilding
# main.tex. Scoped to papers/ so the tracked .log/.out run logs elsewhere
# (experiments/, reproductions/*) are unaffected. The compiled main.pdf is
# intentionally NOT ignored.
